nodes.text: A male Yuuzhan Vong assassin was aboard Harrar's priestship in 25 ABY, and demonstrated the effects of bo'tous to high ranked Yuuzhan Vong. He entered an inhibition field where prisoners were being kept, and emptied his lungs of the bo'tous inside them. However, although all of the prisoners died, the assassin could not get out of the field, and he died as well.
